Avec sa capacité à sentir toute odeur, il trouve sans
faillir de la nourriture enfouie dans le sol.

Although it is a
good climber, it
prefers to snap trees with its
forelegs and eat
fallen BERRIES.

With its ability
to distinguish any
aroma, it unfail­ ingly finds all
food buried deep
underground.

Although it has a
large body, it is
quite skilled at climbing trees. It
eats and sleeps in
the treetops.

In the forests inhabited by URSARING,
it is said that there are many streams
and towering trees where they gather food. This POKéMON walks
through its forest gathering food
every day.

In forests, it is said that there are many
streams and towering trees where an
URSARING gathers food. It walks through
its forest collecting food every day.

it unfailingly finds all food buried deep
underground.

scratches on trees that bear

どんな　においも　かぎわける。
じめんふかくに　うまっている
たべものも　のこらず　みつけだす。

어떠한 냄새라도 구별할 수 있다.
땅속 깊이 파묻혀 있는
먹이도 남김없이 찾아낸다.

Da es alle Gerüche perfekt unterscheiden kann,
findet es sogar Nahrung, die tief im Erdreich ist.

Capaz de percibir cualquier tipo de aroma, encuentra
sin problemas todo alimento enterrado bajo tierra.

Con la sua capacità di distinguere qualsiasi odore,
trova cibo nel terreno anche a grandi profondità.

With its ability to distinguish any aroma, it
unfailingly finds all food buried deep underground.

どんな　においも　かぎわける。
地面深くに　埋まっている
食べ物も　残らず　見つけ出す。

おおきな　からだの　もちぬしだが
きのぼりが　じょうずで　きの　うえで
エサを　たべたり　ねたりする。

커다란 몸집을 가졌지만
나무 타기를 잘하여 나무 위에서
먹이를 먹거나 잔다.

Bien que d’une large corpulence, il grimpe aux arbres
pour s’y nourrir et y dormir.

Trotz seines riesigen Körpers ist es ein guter Kletterer.
Es frisst und schläft in Baumkronen.

Aunque es muy grande, no se le da nada mal lo de
trepar árboles. Come y duerme en las copas.

Nonostante la stazza, è abile ad arrampicarsi in cima
agli alberi, dove mangia e dorme.

Although it has a large body, it is quite skilled at
climbing trees. It eats and sleeps in the treetops.

大きな　体の　持ち主だが
木登りが　上手で　木の　上で
エサを　食べたり　寝たりする。

もりの　なかには　リングマが　エサあつめを　する
たいぼくや　おがわが　あちこちに　あると　いう。
まいにち　エサを　あつめて　もりを　あるく。

숲 속에는 링곰이 먹이를 수집하는
큰 나무나 시냇가가 여기저기에 있다고 한다.
매일 먹이를 모으며 숲을 걷는다.

On dit que les Ursaring trouvent leur nourriture dans les cours
d’eau et les grands arbres des forêts où ils habitent.
Ce Pokémon erre dans la forêt toute la journée pour chercher
de la nourriture.

In den von Ursaring bewohnten Wäldern gibt es viele Flüsse
und hohe Bäume, in denen es Nahrung findet. Dieses Pokémon
läuft täglich durch den Wald, um nach Essbarem zu suchen.

En los bosques habitados por Ursaring, dicen que abundan
los arroyos y árboles gigantes en los que guardan su
alimento. Este Pokémon se dedica todos los días a pasear
por el bosque para buscar comida y guardarla.

Si dice che nelle foreste in cui vive Ursaring ci siano molti
corsi d’acqua e alberi giganti dove questo Pokémon
nasconde le proprie scorte di cibo. Ogni giorno si aggira
nella foresta alla ricerca di alimenti.

In the forests inhabited by Ursaring, it is said that there are
many streams and towering trees where they gather food.
This Pokémon walks through its forest gathering food
every day.

森の　中には　リングマが　エサ集めを　する
大木や　小川が　あちこちに　あると　いう。
毎日　エサを　集めて　森を　歩く。
